query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('executable-jar',
'fgets',
'gnu',
'google-docs',
'http-get',
'modeling',
'ngfor',
'popover',
'portable-class-library',
'soa',
'sql-server-express',
'zoo');
